{"tid":2213551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中資大買北海道土地，日媒：恐成一帶一路據點","createTime":"2020-09-22T15:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T05:00:12.000Z","uid":58841,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"826e188880332ea617155bcb225ee9eec4e78114","tid":2213551,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"日本產經新聞社旗下的富士晚報指出，甫上台的菅義偉政府應處理的優先議題包括正視外資收購日本土地一事，尤其是中国人大買北海道土地，企圖做為中國「一帶一路」的據點。<br />\n<br />\n日本首相菅義偉所組的內閣 16 日上路，菅義偉表示施政的最優先課題是早日讓武漢肺炎疫情平息與重振經濟，此外就是進行行政與規制的改革。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/09/22/china-capital-hokkaido-land/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F09%2F22%2Fchina-capital-hokkaido-land%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I24gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=99cd97f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/09/22/china-capital-hokkaido-land/</a>"},{"pid":"c76ec7a92ae4a3a5bc54d571bceac4c1a1730f4d","tid":2213551,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"中國，台灣，蒙古，朝鮮，韓國，越南，日本<br />\n<br />\n大東亞共榮圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc59a79c1a41cd045d0464ed38d7e2f25812ab6","tid":2213551,"uid":58841,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OgwcTi936Rg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOgwcTi936Rg&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I24gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=e41fa2e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OgwcTi936Rg</a><br />\n痴撚線 安倍之前做緊乜撚野去到菅義偉先肯醒<br />\n你話今日香港後日台灣大後日北海道真係完全唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f615ef246eb8f23459edf000f5ac2d0a76fbcf","tid":2213551,"uid":34602,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"fbc59a79c1a41cd045d0464ed38d7e2f25812ab6","tid":2213551,"uid":58841,"like":16,"dislike":1,"